race.comment: The well-related LARRIKIN ROGUE (9) (half to G3 winner Shamalia) was well in the betting at Eagle Farm at the latest effort but just ran into one better on that occasion. Steps up to the mile journey now and will give backers a sight. FREE CARRY (1) grows a leg for hoop Jones who has four wins and four placings from 11 steers. Maps well for this from gate two and can make his presence felt. The honest EXCEED SPEED (4) has a solid record here with a win and three placings from six spins and is usually thereabouts. A must for the multiples. EXPRESS PAYMENT (3) was a touch plain last time out but the form prior was good enough for a race like this. Worth another chance. BLAZEN BOOTS (7) is a four-time winner around this circuit and comes into calculations.
